<title>GERMANY: SAP product handles Deutsche Post payroll.</title>
<headline>SAP product handles Deutsche Post payroll.</headline>
<dateline>WALLDORF, Germany 1997-02-07</dateline>
<text>
<p>German business software developer SAP AG said on Friday the German post office has begun using SAP's R/3 software to manage its payroll.</p>
<p>The R/3 installation, SAP's largest ever for a personnel department, would process pay checks and accounting for more than 300,000 employees of Deutsche Post AG, SAP said.</p>
<p>SAP and Deutsche Post expected to cooperate on a pension system later this year.</p>
